column18: 01/14/2012: Gunmen attacked a Chinese boat carrying wood on the Mekong River in Laos. No one was injured in the attack, the first since China had begun to protect shipping with joint patrols. No group claimed responsibility for the incident.
column108: It is unknown if any property was damaged in this attack.
column126: \\"\"China says shots fired at cargo boat on Mekong"
